                                <span>What Products And Services Does Al Hilal Offer?</span>
                                <img src="~/Content/assets/images/plus.png" class="faq-icon">
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body teal-bg text-white">
                                Al Hilal is a full-service premium product retailer offering a wide range of authentic Arabian products including dates, honey, spices, and curated gift boxes.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3 faq-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button fw-semibold collapsed d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span>Do They Provide Delivery Within Karachi?</span>
                                <img src="~/Content/assets/images/plus.png" class="faq-icon">
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body teal-bg text-white">
                                Yes, we provide delivery within Karachi city limits.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3 faq-card">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button fw-semibold collapsed d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3" aria-expanded="false">
                                <span>How Do I Place An Order?</span>
                                <img src="~/Content/assets/images/plus.png" class="faq-icon">
                            </button>
                        </h2>
